==English==
===Etymology===
Effing is for f'ing, a euphemism for '[[fucking]]';
Blinding is a euphemism for '[[bloody]]'

===Verb form===
'''effing and blinding'''

#[[Present participle]] of '''to [[eff and blind]]'''.

===Noun===
'''effing and blinding''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

#[[swearing]], [[cursing]].
#:''Much '''effing and blinding''' could be heard from the fans when they discovered that their team had lost.''